{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"stepbystep","title":"stepbystep","subLink":null},{"id":"registerthemodule","title":"Register The Module","subLink":[]},{"id":"designthejson","title":"Design the Json","subLink":[]},{"id":"createtheform","title":"Create the Form","subLink":[]},{"id":"htmlimplementation","title":"Html Implementation","subLink":[]}],"title":"Step By Step Design","description":"","validatorType":"template-driven","validationTypeTitle":"Template Driven Decorator","type":"simple","category":"dynamic-forms","subCategory":null,"linkTitle":"stepbystep","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class='row page-section' id= 'registerthemodule'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Register The Module<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#registerthemodule'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >First You need to import the <span class='highlighted'>RxDynamicReactiveFormsModule</span> in the app module.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-module-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'designthejson'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Design the Json<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#designthejson'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The second step is to define the json data which comes from the server. The Json data is stored in the form of <span class='highlighted'>serverData</span>.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-serverData-component\"></div>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >To Bind the formControl to the user interface, you have to define in the <span class='highlighted'>uiBindings</span>.</p>\r\n<blockquote class='showHideElement' ><p>Note : If you want to change the order of the formControls in the user Interface. You must do it in <span class='highlighted'>uiBindings</span></p></blockquote>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-ui-component\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'createtheform'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Create the Form<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#createtheform'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The Third Step is to create a form using <span class='highlighted'>dynamicForm</span> method of <span class='highlighted'>RxFormBuilder</span>. In that you pass the serverData and dynamicFormConfiguration as below.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-form-component\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'htmlimplementation'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Html Implementation<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#htmlimplementation'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The Fourth and last step is to pass the html tag in the template using <span class='highlighted'>rxweb-dynamic-form</span> and pass the dynamicFormBuildConfig as <span class='highlighted'>rxDynamicForm</span> in the form tag</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-form-html\"></div>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-complete\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}